🇺🇦🇺🇦🇺🇦

With this shirt we want to give humanitarian aid to people suffering from the war: families, children, refugees, medics. For every shirt that is purchased for the minimum price 10€ will go directly to the Ministry of Social Policy of Ukraine and will be spent on food, shelter, medicine, clothes and other help for refugees. If you want to donate more you can do so by typing your own "price" – every additional cent will be donated!

For more information see: https://war.ukraine.ua/support-ukraine

